'''堅尼街'''（官方路牌<ref>{{cite web|author=葉清菲 |date={{dts|||}} |title=鏡頭下的紐約唐人街 似曾相識如此美麗（圖） |url=https://www.sinovision.net/portal.php?mod=view&aid=42966 |website=[[美國中文網|美國中文網]] |quote=[圖中路牌] CANAL ST -{堅尼街}- [圖下説明] 堅尼街是唐人街的‘心髒’。 |access-date={{dts|2019|9|5}} |language=zh}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Amengual |first=Bartomeu |date={{dts|2013|10|1}} |title=Canal Street sign in Englis and Chinese. Chinatown, New York City Stock Photo: 61078078 |url=https://www.alamy.com/canal-street-sign-in-englis-and-chinese-chinatown-new-york-city-usa-image61078078.html |type=照片 |website=[[Alamy|Alamy]] |quote=[圖中路牌] CANAL ST -{堅尼街}- |access-date={{dts|2019|9|4}} |language=en}}</ref>，{{lang-en|Canal Street}}，簡稱：{{lang|en|Canal}}，另譯'''運河街'''<ref>{{cite web |last=Satow |first=Julie |date={{dts|2014|3|7}} |title=When Age Belies Buying Power |trans-title=那些年輕的百萬富豪喜歡買什麼房？ |url=https://cn.nytimes.com/real-estate/20140307/t07youngbuyers/dual/ |website=[[紐約時報中文網|紐約時報中文網]] |quote=他們選擇了運河街 (Canal Street)，而避開公園大道 (Park Avenue)； |access-date={{dts|2019|9|5}} |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2019-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905151418/https://cn.nytimes.com/real-estate/20140307/t07youngbuyers/dual/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Chen |first=Elaine |title=As Manhattan's Chinatown Changes, Food Vendors Keep a Bit of the Old With the New |trans-title=新與舊、變與不變：紐約唐人街的食物與人 |url=https://cn.nytimes.com/style/20181220/china-town-food/dual/ |website=紐約時報中文網 |date={{dts|2018|12|20}} |quote=Her sister and brother run a similar stand around the corner farther east on Canal. [她有兄弟姐妹在運河街往東更遠的拐角處經營著一個類似的攤位。] |access-date={{dts|2019|9|2}} |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903012037/https://cn.nytimes.com/style/20181220/china-town-food/dual/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是[[美國|美國]][[紐約州|紐約州]][[紐約市|紐約市]][[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]一條東西走向的主要街道，橫穿[[曼哈頓下城|曼哈頓下城]]，向西經[[荷蘭隧道|荷蘭隧道]]直達[[新澤西州|新澤西州]][[澤西市|澤西市]]，向東經[[曼哈頓大橋|曼哈頓大橋]]通往紐約市[[布魯克林區|布魯克林區]]。它是[[曼哈頓華埠|曼哈頓華埠]]的主要脊柱，並將其與[[小意大利_(曼哈頓)|小意大利]]分隔開來，同時構成[[紐約蘇豪區|蘇豪區]]的南部邊界以及[[翠貝卡|翠貝卡]]的北部邊界。

堅尼街原爲一條開挖於19世紀初的運河，用以將遭受嚴重汙染的池水排入[[哈得遜河|哈得遜河]]。池塘大約於1813年或1815年被填平，爾後紐約市於1820年填河築路。

現在的堅尼街是一處繁華商業區，店鋪房租相比曼哈頓其他地段較爲低廉，其東段以銀行和珠寶店爲主。這條街同時也是曼哈頓華埠的主要珠寶商圈<ref>{{cite book|last=Zhou |first=Min |title=Chinatown: The Socioeconomic Potential of an Urban Enclave |edition=[[電子書|電子書]] |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZcBxKK0cljcC&pg=PA106 |page=106 |publisher={{link-en|天普大學出版社|Temple University Press}} |location=[[費城|費城]] |date={{dts|2010||}} |orig-year={{dts|1992|5|19}} |ISBN=978-1-4399-0417-6 |access-date={{dts|2019|9|2}} |language=en}}</ref>，遊客及當地居民時常光顧露天大排檔和廉價商店。儘管常有警察突擊搜查，仿冒品仍廣泛售於其中。<ref>{{cite web |last=Hauser |first=Christine |title=City Agents Shut Down 32 Vendors of Fake Items |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2008/02/27/nyregion/27chinatown.html |website=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]] |date={{dts|2008|2|27}} |access-date={{dts|2019|9|2}} |language=en-US |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903012038/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/02/27/nyregion/27chinatown.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Kalman |first1=Alex |last2=Sinreich |first2=Lola |title=New York's Street of Schemes |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/01/17/opinion/17kalman.html |website=紐約時報 |date={{dts|2010|1|16}} |access-date={{dts|2019|9|2}} |language=en-US |archive-date=2019-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190903012036/https://www.nytimes.com/2010/01/17/opinion/17kalman.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

